Title: Masmi Organic Cotton Applicator Superplus Tampons
Description: The Combo contains 2 packs of Masmi Applicator Superplus Tampons (with each containing 14 pieces individually wrapped). Ideal for heavy to extra heavy flow days. 100% Pure Certified Organic Cotton Absorbent Core. Hypoallergenic to reduce the risks of irritation and allergy. Special security veil covering the absorbent core to stop the fibres sticking inside women's body during the tampon removal. Cardboard applicator with rounded end tip for a comfortable and soft insertion plus 100% BIODEGRADABLE. Removal Cord is totally sewed to the absorbent core. Wrapped individually for easy carrying and access. Perfume and superabsorbent free. Viscose/ Rayon free absorbent core. No Chlorine or Dioxin used in the Bleaching process. Gynaecologists, midwives and obstetricians recommend the use of natural cotton products for your intimate hygiene. Always use the lowest absorbency tampon to meet your needs. Tampons are associated to the Toxic Shock Syndrome (TSS). TSS is a rare but serious disease. For your Health and Safety read and save the enclosed information.

Floral-woody Heart Note This Eau de Parfum is a blend of fresh orchid and patchouli at the heart. Ambery-musky Base Note Base notes of white musk and white amber leave you with an invigorating feel.

Title: Carolina Herrera 212 Sexy EDT  -  50 ml(For Men)
Description: Carolina Herrera introduces 212 Sexy Eau de Toilette for the debonair man who believes in spreading his alluring charm all the way. This enticing fragrance is emphatically masculine and leaves behind a light and invigorating fragrance. Top Note The perfect amalgam of energetic mandarin, ginger and fresh bergamot, the aroma of this perfume finds solace in the top note. Heart Note Carolina Herrera gives this perfume a provocative touch with a heart of tonka beans, green pepper, floral petal and cardamom that spread the heavenly floral aroma around. Base Note Indulge in a relaxing mood as the base notes of bourbon vanilla, amber, gaiac wood, musk and sandalwood spread that soothing aura.

Title: Brut Oceans Aftershave  -  100 ml(For Men)
Description: He applies himself wholly to the task in hand - the shaving foam parts slightly where his deep dimples make themselves prominent. As his brow furrows in concentration, the razor does its ritualistic dance over the rugged line of his jaw. The ceremonious routine is completed with a splash of Brut Oceans Aftershave. With light, refreshing notes that sting like the biting notes of a salty breeze blowing in from the sea, Brut Oceans Aftershave is the redolence of the man who settles for nothing less that the perfect. The mass premium fragrance soothes razor burn and leaves the skin with a smooth after note. The minty blue of the aftershave peeks out from a simple flacon that fits right into a regular shaving kit. Make things interesting with the spicy, fresh sensation that Brut Oceans Aftershave leaves behind.

Title: Ralph Lauren Safari EDT Natural Spray - 125 ml(For Men)
Description: With an essence of floral and citrus notes, this perfume from Ralph Lauren has a dash of freshness and suits the different facets of your persona. Top Note Wear this perfume and lose yourself in its exotic scent that is warmed with a top note of neroli, aldehyde, artemisia, lavender, lemon, coriander, green notes and bergamot. Heart Note Imbibing the freshness of cyclamen, jasmine, rose, carnation, cinnamon and tarragon, this perfume is eternally provocative and leaves everybody around you at awe. Base Note The base note of amber, musk, leather, sandalwood, oakmoss, patchouli and cedar is deep and will keep you energetic all day.

Title: Swiss Army Altitude EDT  -  100 ml(For Men)

This crisp and refreshing Eau de Toilette uplifts your spirits with its smooth yet distinctive sparkle. The woody, aromatic Altitude opens with a top note of fresh Virginia cedar and juniper berries and trails into a heart note of sage and mint. The woody base note adds a sophisticated charm to the fragrance. Ideal for daily wear, this signature perfume perfectly adheres to the sporty, athletic streak in you.

Title: Axe Signature Mysterious Body Perfume - 122 ml(For Men)
